Body:
with expected_protocol(ik.hp.HP3456a, ['HO0T4SO1', 'S1F1W1STNT3',
    'S0F4W1STNT3', 'S0F1W1STNT3', 'W1STNT3'], ['+00.00000E-3',
    '+000.1010E+0', '+000.0002E-3', '+000.0002E-3'], sep='\r') as dmm:
    assert dmm.measure(dmm.Mode.ratio_dcv_dcv) == 0
    assert dmm.measure(dmm.Mode.resistance_2wire) == +0.101 * u.ohm
    assert dmm.measure(dmm.Mode.dcv) == +2e-07 * u.volt
    assert dmm.measure() == +2e-07
